                        "text": "Develop the other skills: ",
                        "list": [
                            {
                                "text": "<strong>Cognitive development: </strong> identify numbers and count."
                            },
                            {
                                "text": "<strong>Gross motor skills: </strong> movement following the song, clap hands one time, one step forward, one step backward, raise thumb up, raise thumb down.."
                            },
                            {
                                "text": "<strong>Fine motor skills:</strong> interactive games"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
